{"tid":1737750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再信警察同敵對既人啦","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:00:38.000Z","uid":28264,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"defe786f393c4e323381c84b1bb17593b63330e3","tid":1737750,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"班狗根本就沒誠信可言<br />\n由中大到理大 咁多次啦 唔好再信佢地<br />\n我明好多時大家都好驚 會唔小心信左班狗 之後就中伏<br />\n但經歷左咁多 真係點都唔可以再相信<br />\n果D乜撚野泛民既人又好 曾鈺成又好 都唔好信<br />\n曾鈺成雖然係一個大家都尊重既人 但一日共產黨一世共產黨 都係撚樣黎<br />\n泛民?屌你老母啦 如果10幾年前泛民係做到野 今日唔洗咁多後生仔要企出黎<br />\n2者都係撚樣黎 一樣唔可信<br />\n求下大家 點都好 唔好再信班狗 泛民同曾鈺成果D撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e6474237b51a5371f1e6c1dfce921420908283","tid":1737750,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ecdbf08b1ec0c7556fdb4a7ab42e1d0f872efb","tid":1737750,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8f2b6b50d0ff42313ac376f721064d289ae5cc","tid":1737750,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7e75fed1c43195be2a2f514da13c4cedbf3bc4","tid":1737750,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,